OL,3,CResidents warn council's new
OL,4,Cpedestrian crossing design could put
OL,5,Clives at risk
OL,7,FParents and drivers are warning
OL,8,Fsomeone could be seriously injured or
OL,9,Fkilled at a busy junction near
OL,10,FWokingham because of the unusual
OL,11,Fdesign of the pedestrian crossings.
OL,13,FThe intersection in Finchampstead has
OL,14,Fbeen painted with large white leaves
OL,15,Fshowing where people can cross the
OL,16,Froads, instead of a traditional zebra
OL,17,Fcrossing design.
