OL,3,CResidents warn council's new
OL,4,Cpedestrian crossing design could put
OL,5,Clives at risk
OL,7,FThe council removed two mini
OL,8,Froundabouts at California Crossroads
OL,9,Fand replaced them with the leaf design
OL,10,Fon the road surface.
OL,12,FWhen viewed from above, the new design
OL,13,Fon the road is more clear.
OL,15,FHowever, some motorists say that
OL,16,Fwithout an obvious roundabout centre
OL,17,Fto move around, vehicles are cutting
OL,18,Fstraight across to make their turns
OL,19,Fand many are not aware that the white
OL,20,Fpainted leaves are the pedestrian
OL,21,Fcrossings.
