OL,4,Cpedestrian crossing design could put
OL,5,Clives at risk
OL,7,FReuben Miles-Brar, a local shop-owner,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Previously there were two
OL,9,Froundabouts and they've decided to
OL,10,Feradicate them and add in these
OL,11,Fleaves. I've seen children trying to
OL,12,Fjump across the maple leaves thinking
OL,13,Fit is hopscotch.
OL,15,F"Just a minute ago, as I pulled up, it
OL,16,Fwas chaos here with three cars. No-one
OL,17,Fknows where they're meant to be, and
OL,18,Fthey are pulling up next to one
OL,19,Fanother and shouting at one another
OL,20,Fthrough their windows. It causes chaos
OL,21,Fand frustration."
