OL,3,CResidents warn council's new
OL,4,Cpedestrian crossing design could put
OL,5,Clives at risk
OL,7,FLocal driving instructor, Andrew Rock,
OL,8,Ffrom X-tra Mile Academy, also has
OL,9,Fconcerns.
OL,11,FHe said: "Even as instructors, some of
OL,12,Fus have come here and it is not always
OL,13,Fquite clear whether or not it is a
OL,14,Fcrossing, who gives way and who has
OL,15,Fpriority.
OL,17,F"Safety is one of the crucial things
OL,18,Fwe have to address when teaching and
OL,19,Fif there is any ambiguity, it makes it
OL,20,Fvery difficult for the pupils to know
OL,21,Fwhat to do and how to teach them."
